{"tid":1078002,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[NBA] 點解咁憎勇士？","createTime":"2019-03-26T03:48:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T05:30:41.000Z","uid":231466,"like":8,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"f626a7c3a885112603750b975a1eb76e46886c72","tid":1078002,"uid":231466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T03:48:25.000Z","msg":"平時同fd傾波個陣<br />\n一聽到自己鐘意勇士就好似比人笑咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n問番佢地鐘意邊隊<br />\n佢地就話公牛潮人 個樣仲要好有優越感<br />\n<br />\n的確勇士排面上五星戰隊好似屈左人機<br />\n咁佢地都係3個自家球星養出黎<br />\n唔通冇努力過話贏就贏<br />\n<br />\n其實無論邊隊 以前到而家都會靠球星<br />\n其實隊隊都會想組巨頭 <br />\n講緊以前熱火 湖人 公牛都3巨頭以上<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62af26ce2b3e907eadb93f35ea1d5167749cb42e","tid":1078002,"uid":231102,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T03:49:54.000Z","msg":"因為KD"},{"pid":"69382ca7d27b0f063c7d4f8753d93ce794552f7a","tid":1078002,"uid":217336,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T03:53:01.000Z","msg":"似係你d fd 憎你多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ae80fa0cf55e36afaf16bdacbeaa3c9979e961e","tid":1078002,"uid":13480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T03:53:50.000Z","msg":"以前熱火湖人都好多haters"},{"pid":"7b65cad2f6100224d80362ea2b9fdd20cd539c26","tid":1078002,"uid":555,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T03:54:10.000Z","msg":"勁咪憎囉"},{"pid":"53f954f10cf200f1220d8cd5b8c9765641ea7ae1","tid":1078002,"uid":18389,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T03:54:14.000Z","msg":"2015定2017忽然fans?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2a202a4a7754fa39b5519574c7ba153055b6c6b","tid":10780